snippet.title: The Raging Cinema Podcast
snippet.description: The Raging Cinema Podcast, hosted by Matthew Perry, starring Salvatore Blandina and Ryan Helterhoff. Sal and Ryan's love of the silver screen is what led to this podcast's creation. Both men have goals of working within the film industry, and their chance to discuss the passions they have starting here.
